---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fermier Créatif | Autonomie</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#fdfcfb] text-stone-900">

    <nav class="p-8 flex justify-between items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter border-b-4 border-green-600">FERMIER CRÉATIF</div>
        <div class="hidden md:block space-x-8 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-500">
            <a href="#blog" class="hover:text-green-600">Le Blog</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-green-600">À Propos</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-40">
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-[120px] font-[900] leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter mb-8">
            CULTIVER <br/> <span class="text-green-600 italic">DEMAIN.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-stone-500 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            De la gestion des sols argileux à l'automatisation de la serre. 
            Découvrez nos expériences d'autonomie à Notre-Dame-de-l'Île-Perrot.
        </p>
    </header>

    <main id="blog" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t border-stone-200">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-stone-400 mb-12">Dossiers Récents</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
            <a href="/blog/champignons" class="group">
                <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-stone-200 rounded-2xl mb-6 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-full h-full bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504618223053-559bdef9dd5a?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000')] bg-cover bg-center group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold group-hover:text-green-600 transition">Culture de Champignons</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-500 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Apprendre à cultiver pleurotes et hydnes hérissons à la maison.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/blog/coccinelles" class="group">
                <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-stone-200 rounded-2xl mb-6 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-full h-full bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555037015-1498966bcd7c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000')] bg-cover bg-center group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold group-hover:text-green-600 transition">Lutte Biologique</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-500 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Utiliser les coccinelles pour protéger vos semis de piments forts.</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="p-20 text-center text-stone-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em]">
        &copy; 2026 Fermier Créatif
    </footer>

</body>
</html>